OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and bright for many, with
OL,6,Fsunny spells. Much of Scotland will be
OL,7,Fcloudy, with outbreaks of rain across
OL,8,Fthe northwest. Southeast England will
OL,9,Falso be rather cloudy, with some
OL,10,Fshowers. Warm for many, but fresher in
OL,11,Fthe far north.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain clearing to leave a dry
OL,14,Fevening and night, with clear spells.
OL,15,FSome fog developing during the early
OL,16,Fhours in the southwest. Rain arriving
OL,17,Finto the far northwest towards dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
