OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FRain, heavy at times, will
OL,6,Fmove eastwards across Scotland and
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland, moving across
OL,8,FEngland and Wales during the evening
OL,9,Fand overnight. Ahead of this, plenty
OL,10,Fof warm sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
